From 319489424a3fb4cfdc5488337669f89c276e8b82 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 6 Apr 2026 22:56:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(appstore): add plugin removal confirmation with data
 preservation option

Replace browser confirm() dialog with a styled Bootstrap Modal that shows
plugin data size and lets users choose whether to keep or delete plugin
configuration and data files. Default is to preserve data (safe default).

Adds GET /appstore/datasize/:name endpoint to calculate plugin data size,
and extends the remove endpoint to accept a deleteData parameter.

